snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Jason Momoa Calling Her Out!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Reacts To Jason Momoa Calling Her Out!
Johnny Depp allegedly assaulted Amber Heard physically and emotionally, according to Amber Heard. In 2015, their first legal struggle resulted in a restraining order against Johnny Depp, but it was also at this time when the blurred lines began. Johnny's assertion that Amber Heard lied about her black eye in court was corroborated by Amber's stylist.
